  "title": "Business Development Manager[Landlord Leasing /Landlord agency/ interior fitting out / renovation/ find new client/ commercial and government projects]",
  "description": "<p>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</p>\n<p>Key Responsibilities</p>\n<p>• Obtain new clients and secure potential commercial and government projects.</p>\n<p>• Lead business growth by identifying and cultivating new opportunities to expand the company's portfolio and market presence.</p>\n<p>• Manage sales inquiries for commercial and government projects.</p>\n<p>• Consult with clients to ascertain requirements and needs.</p>\n<p>• Submit tenders and negotiate prices with clients.</p>\n<p>• Organize workflow to meet client deadlines for handover.</p>\n<p>• Collaborate with designers, project managers, QS team, and purchasing team to ensure high-quality project completion, prioritize client satisfaction, and execute projects smoothly.</p>",
